<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard2.0</TargetFramework>
    <RootNamespace>NKristek.Smaragd</RootNamespace>
    <AssemblyName>NKristek.Smaragd</AssemblyName>
    <Version>3.0</Version>
    <Description>Base classes for implementing an C# .NET application using the MVVM architecture</Description>
    <Company>nkristek</Company>
    <Authors>nkristek</Authors>
    <Product>Smaragd</Product>
    <PackageId>NKristek.Smaragd</PackageId>
    <Copyright>Copyright Â©  2018 Niclas Kristek</Copyright>
    <PackageLicenseUrl>https://github.com/nkristek/Smaragd/blob/master/LICENSE</PackageLicenseUrl>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/nkristek/Smaragd</PackageProjectUrl>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/nkristek/Smaragd.git</RepositoryUrl>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageTags></PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>This release introduces better code coverage and fixes potential bugs. This is a major release since there are sourcebreaking changes, please read the readme.

Changes include:

CommandCanExecuteSourceAttribute was renamend to CanExecuteSourceAttribute and is now only allowed on ICommand.CanExecute() in classes implementing IRaiseCanExecuteChanged.

PropertySourceCollectionAttribute and CommandCanExecuteSourceCollectionAttribute were removed with no replacement as part of a refactoring to reduce code complexity and potential of bugs.

AsyncCommand, AsyncRelayCommand, Command and RelayCommand were removed, it is recommended to use AsyncViewModelCommand or ViewModelCommand instead.

The ViewModel.Children property was removed, consequential ChildViewModelAttribute and ChildViewModelCollectionAttribute were also removed.

In TreeViewModel, if children are present, the TreeChildren property should be overriden for IsChecked to work properly.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <NeutralLanguage>en</NeutralLanguage>
    <AssemblyVersion>3.0.0.0</AssemblyVersion>
    <FileVersion>3.0.0.0</FileVersion>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='Release|AnyCPU'">
    <LangVersion>latest</LangVersion>
    <DocumentationFile>bin\Release\netstandard2.0\NKristek.Smaragd.xml</DocumentationFile>
  </PropertyGroup>

</Project>
